Class ComparatorDistanceBased

    java.util.Comparator<ImageContainer>

    public class ComparatorDistanceBased
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<ImageContainer>
    This comparator uses distances to a given query image computed by a given distance metric to compare two images.
